<li class="expanded"><a href="/topics/emergency-police-mil">Public Safety</a><ul class="menu">
<li class="leaf"><a href="/topics/communication-interoperabillity">Communication interoperabillity</a></li>
<li class="leaf"><a href="/topics/emergency-services">Emergency services</a></li>
<li class="leaf"><a href="/topics/emergency-medical-services">Emergency medical services</a></li>
<li class="leaf"><a href="/topics/fire">Fire</a></li>
<li class="leaf"><a href="/topics/emergency-first-response">First response</a></li>
<li class="leaf"><a href="/topics/ieds">IEDs</a></li>
